extends.description:
Assigns a unique key to an element for DOM diffing.
Crucial inside loops to ensure elements are updated correctly and state is preserved.

### Example
```html
@foreach(items as item)
    <div wire:key="item-{{ item.id }}">
        {{ item.name }}
    </div>
@endforeach
```

